    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997-generation Carrera S features the high-revving 3.8L flat-six M97 powerplant, delivering linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), optimizing damping rates for superior lateral grip and composure. Mechanical highlights include a Variocam Plus valve timing system and a dry-sump lubrication setup for consistent oil pressure under high-G loads. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers paired with cross-drilled rotors, ensuring minimal thermal fade and excellent pedal modulation. While the exterior displays a light patina reflective of its enthusiast history, the drivetrain remains robust with recent service to the cooling system and shift linkages. This is a mechanically sound example of a modern classic, offering visceral feedback and exceptional torsional rigidity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
