    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a keen eye might spot a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats have been treated regularly, showing only slight softening on the driver's side bolster. Every button, dial, and screen functions exactly as intended, including the dual-zone climate control and the premium sound system. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has followed a strict maintenance schedule with synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. Recent service includes a fresh set of all-season tires with excellent tread remaining and a complete brake pad replacement. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and seamless. This is a solid, honest car that has been loved and is ready for its next chapter.",
